## 3. Quy tắc kiến trúc

### 3.1. Dependency Rule

```
Pages → PageModels → Services → Repositories → DbContext
```

**Nguyên tắc:**
- PageModels inject Services (không inject Repositories trực tiếp)
- Services inject Repositories
- Repositories inject DbContext
- Không bao giờ inject DbContext trong PageModels

```csharp
// ✅ Đúng: Inject Service vào PageModel
public class IndexModel : PageModel
{
    private readonly IUserService _userService;
    public IndexModel(IUserService userService)
    {
        _userService = userService;
    }
}

// ❌ Sai: Inject Repository trực tiếp vào PageModel
public class IndexModel : PageModel
{
    private readonly ApplicationDbContext _context; // KHÔNG LÀM THẾ NÀY
}
```

### 3.2. Service Layer

```csharp
// ✅ Đúng: Business logic trong Service
public class RequestService : IRequestService
{
    public async Task<Request> CreateRequest(RequestCreateDto dto)
    {
        // Validate business rules
        if (dto.RequestType == RequestType.Maintenance && dto.Priority == Priority.Low)
        {
            throw new BusinessRuleException("Maintenance requests must have minimum Normal priority");
        }
        // Gọi repository
        return await _requestRepository.Create(dto);
    }
}
```

### 3.3. Repository Layer

```csharp
// ✅ Đúng: Generic Repository pattern
public class RequestRepository : IRequestRepository
{
    public async Task<Request> GetByIdAsync(int id)
    {
        return await _context.Requests
            .Include(r => r.User)
            .Include(r => r.Comments)
            .FirstOrDefaultAsync(r => r.Id == id);
    }
}
```

